data.description: Welcome to 843 Trilby, nestled in the picturesque Bella Vista community! This charming two-story residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience, presenting an ideal opportunity for those seeking a vibrant and welcoming neighborhood to call home.  Boasting 4 bedrooms, all conveniently located upstairs, this home provides ample space for relaxation and privacy. The primary bedroom offers a tranquil retreat with its spacious layout, while the secondary bedrooms have been freshly painted, ready to reflect your personal style.  Step inside to discover modern comforts thoughtfully integrated throughout. In July 2023, a state-of-the-art HVAC system with a media air filter system was installed, ensuring optimal indoor air quality and year-round comfort. The kitchen shines with recent upgrades, including a dishwasher, stove, and microwave installed in May 2023, perfect for culinary enthusiasts and busy lives alike.  Beyond its interior features, this residence offers practical amenities designed to enhance your lifestyle. A water softener system promises softened water for everyday use, while the seller's generous contribution of up to $5000 for a carpet allowance on an approved offer allows you to customize the space to your liking.  Situated in a highly sought-after location, residents enjoy close proximity to a variety of amenities. Commuters will appreciate easy access to the nearby JBSA Lackland military base, as well as major thoroughfares such as Interstate 1604 and 211. Explore a wealth of retail shops, restaurants, and entertainment options just moments away, making everyday errands and weekend outings a breeze.  Bella Vista itself is renowned for its friendly atmosphere and array of community amenities. Spend sunny afternoons lounging by the sparkling pool or watching the little ones explore the playground, fostering a sense of camaraderie and belonging among neighbors.  With top-rated NISD schools and the added benefit of no city taxes, this property offers the perfect combination of comfort, convenience, and value. Don't miss your chance to experience the best of Bella Vista living - schedule your showing today and make this wonderful property your own!
